easily generalizable to an even more flexible\nframework, useful for other '-omics' data, or tabular data in general\n(including medical images after appropriate embedding). A generic\nimplementation is freely available under Apache 2.0 license at\nhttps://github.com/gmrukwa/divik.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Sep 2020 17:50:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 29 Jan 2022 23:46:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 12 Mar 2022 12:07:23 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2022 21:33:50 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2023 20:23:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-19"}
