e asymptotic region. We also predict the critical value of the\nmelt fraction at the transition between the two regions. From these analyses,\nwe draw some conclusions regarding the design procedure for LHTES devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Sep 2020 17:54:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-23"}
