e distortions and show\nthat the use of the one-parameter phenomenological Gaussian damping model for\nfingers-of-God causes significant biases in parameter recovery.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Sep 2020 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 13 Feb 2021 22:42:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-24"}
