up to 3.4x. It\nalso improves considerably the CPs' potential savings by 27.6% on average and\nup to 43.6%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Sep 2020 15:19:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Oct 2020 15:23:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 16 Oct 2020 09:59:20 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 10 Dec 2020 10:48:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-11"}
