from big data, instead it can be\nextracted by PDEs; (iii) there is no need to employ a physics- or\nscale-separation assumptions to build a closure model for PDEs. The advantage\n(i) is demonstrated in the Part I paper [1], while the advantage (ii) is the\nsubject of the current paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Sep 2020 15:24:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Sep 2020 20:06:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-31"}
